    • Method Detail

      • instance

        public static IssueCategoryRegistry instance(org.ocpsoft.rewrite.context.Context context)
        Gets an instance of the IssueCategoryRegistry from a Context. Note that the context variable used might vary depending upon how this class is being used. In some cases, the Context might be a part of the RuleLoaderContext, so that this registry can be used during rule initialization. In other cases, it may be the GraphRewrite event's context.

      • attachToGraph

        public void attachToGraph(GraphContext graphContext)
        Attaches all registered IssueCategorys to the graph. This allows them to be more easily used from rules.

      • loadFromGraph
